  • public class StdExt
extends ConstantsExtension
    My "standard" Xtend Extension, containing all "general" extensions. By importing this class explicitly, I get to also import all other extensions implicitly. I can also add new extensions at any time, and have them directly available everywhere without changes.
    Author:
    monster
